v_products_description_1: A Paradiso classic! This party on a platter starts with a pile of chips, mild Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese layered with your choice of meat, then baked. We finish this Mexican fiesta with jalapenos, tomatoes and a scoop of sour cream topping.

Nibble on your favorite appetizers. 4 slices of lightly crisped chicken flautas, four slices of our ultimate quesadilla and your choice of queso.  Enjoy it with fresh mango pico de gallo and savory jalapeno jelly sauce for dipping.

Delicately seasoned ground beef and melted Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese atop a baked flatbread. Covered with diced tomatoes, fresh poblano peppers, chopped red onions and more cheese! Served with fresh cilantro garnish and your choice of original or mango pico de gallo.

Our three delectable dips served with crisp tortilla chips.

Chili Con Queso: A special blend of Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese, mild chilies and spices combine to make this delicious Mexican fondue.

Queso Blanco: Creamy white queso made with three types of cheese and spices.

Queso Fundido: A traditional Mexican dip of melted spicy cheese served hot from the oven and bubbling with flavor.

Wow! A huge flour tortilla fully stuffed with grilled chicken, bacon, tomato, fresh poblano peppers, and mild Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese. Grilled the Paradiso way and served with sour cream topping.
Pick two of our delectable dips served with crisp tortilla chips.
Made-to-order Haas avocados with house-made pico de gallo. Served with chips and a fresh slice of lime.
Made-to-order Haas avocados and fresh, diced mango mixed with house-made pico de gallo. Served with chips and a fresh slice of lime.
Pick one of our delectable dips served with crisp tortilla chips.

Lightly crisped hand-rolled flour tortillas filled with seasoned shredded chicken, roasted red peppers, grilled corn with mild Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese. Served with jalapeno jelly sauce for dipping.

Try our golden oven-baked flatbread with creamy fundido sauce, grilled chicken, bacon, fresh poblano peppers, Monterey Jack and mozzarella cheese. Topped with mango pico de gallo and fresh chopped cilantro.
Crisp tortilla chips smothered with melted Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese, garnished with diced red onion and jalapeno peppers.
Jumbo buffalo wings tossed with our signature Mango-Habanera buffalo sauce. Served with celery and your choice of ranch or bleu cheese dressing.
Ever so simple, yet so good! A large flour tortilla smothered with mild Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese and baked to perfection.

It's fajita time! Flame grilled and rushed to your table in a sizzling skillet with lightly seasoned caramelized onions, tomatoes, and fresh poblano and red peppers. Served with sides of guacamole, pico de gallo, our Jack and Cheddar cheese blend and sour cream topping. Includes warm flour tortillas and Spanish rice.

It's fajita time! Flame grilled and rushed to your table in a sizzling skillet with lightly seasoned caramelized onions, tomatoes, and fresh poblano and red peppers. Served with sides of guacamole, pico de gallo, our Jack and Cheddar cheese blend and sour cream topping. Includes warm flour tortillas and Spanish rice.

Our vegan, meatless fajita strips are complete protein made with savory blend of nutritious vegetable and grain ingredients (soy, wheat, peas, beets, and carrots) prepared and slow-cooked to have the authentic taste and texture of premium lean meat. Trans fat and cholesterol free.

A hearty salad of shredded lettuce loaded with your choice of meat, a pile of shredded Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese, diced tomatoes and black olives. Lightly sprinkled with Cotija cheese. Served with your choice of dressing.

Tame your appetite with this tostada filled with your choice of meat mixed with rice and mild Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese on a crisp tortilla covered with shredded lettuce, tomatoes, black olives and a scoop of sour cream topping. Lightly sprinkled with Cotija cheese.

Strips of sizzling fajita steak or chicken presented in a large bowl of chilled fresh greens, tomatoes, black olives and mild Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese with sour cream topping. Lightly sprinkled with Cotija cheese.

Warm, marinated and grilled chicken breast served atop freshly mixed greens, our black bean and corn salsa, mild Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese and fresh avocado. Lightly sprinkled with Cotija cheese. Served with your choice of dressing. Try it with our creamy cilantro-lime ranch dressing.

It all begins with a crispy corn tortilla. Then we pile on layers of your choice of favorite fillings and top it with mild Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese, shredded lettuce, olives and tomatoes. Lightly sprinkled with Cotija cheese. Served with your choice of dressing.

This delicious salad is composed of crisp mixed greens, fresh mango pico de gallo, avocado and chopped cilantro. Topped with a warm, grilled mesquite chicken breast. Lightly sprinkled with Cotija cheese. Try it with our creamy cilantro-lime ranch dressing.

Wild-caught Alaskan salmon or seasoned sweet shrimp atop crisp mixed greens, roasted corn salsa and a colorful blend of lightly seasoned and sautéed garden vegetables. Lightly sprinkled with Cotija cheese. Served with fresh avocado and our creamy cilantro ranch dressing.

This combination is bursting with flavor. The treasures of Old Mexico come alive with a mini burrito and home-style chile relleno made with fresh poblano peppers, drenched in red sauce and finished with sour cream topping. Served with Spanish rice and your choice of beans. Substitute Spanish rice and beans with our fresh, seasoned and grilled vegetable mix for .99.

Better bring your appetite to this grande platter! We load your plate with four of our most popular selections: a hand-rolled chicken enchilada, a crispy taco loaded with beef, a home-style chile relleno filled with fresh poblano peppers and Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese and a savory home-style chicken tamale made with stone ground corn masa.
Que Bueno! This trio features our savory cheese enchilada, a home-style chile relleno and a crispy beef taco.

This one put us on the map! Lightly crisped flautas, a special chimi and our famous taco. Served with Spanish rice, and your choice of beans, diced tomatoes and sour cream topping.  Substitute Spanish rice and beans with our fresh, seasoned and grilled vegetable mix for .99.

The name says it all! Enjoy four magnificent selections on one large platter: a Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese enchilada, a crispy beef taco, a savory chicken mini-burrito and a traditional hand-rolled chicken enchilada. A fantastic choice!
Treat your taste buds to this traditional trio. Try a cheese-stuffed enchilada, a chicken tamale and a crispy taco loaded with beef. Muy delicioso!
A real fiesta! A chicken tamale, a mini chicken chimi topped with our fundido sauce and a giant taco. Served with a side of our lightly seasoned veggies and red sauce to top it off.

Muy grande! A large fresh flour tortilla bursting with ground beef and covered with zesty red sauce. Served with a cheese tostada, a home-style chile relleno filled with fresh poblano peppers and served with Spanish rice.
A savory home-style chicken tamale made with stone-ground corn masa and two hand-rolled enchiladas served with your choice of meat or cheese and smothered in zesty red sauce.

Spiced ground beef and mild Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese layered between two corn tortillas and bathed in our lively red sauce. Served with a crispy beef taco, shredded lettuce, tomatoes, and sour cream topping.

Lightly crisped hand-rolled flour tortillas filled with seasoned shredded chicken, roasted red peppers, grilled corn with mild Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese. Served with our jalapeno jelly sauce for dipping. Includes Spanish rice and your choice of beans.

Try this item!  Morsels of seasoned lean pork braised until tender and marinated with savory herbs and spices served on a bed of caramelized onions. Served with Spanish rice and black beans. Garnished with lettuce, mango pico de gallo and a side of flour tortillas.

Wild-caught Alaskan salmon or seasoned sweet shrimp atop crisp mixed greens, roasted corn salsa, and a colorful blend of lightly seasoned and sauteed garden vegetables.  Served with fresh avocado and our creamy cilantro ranch dressing.
You'll love this grande burrito!  A large flour tortilla stuffed with our flavorful seafood filling, topped with seafood sauce and melted mozzarella cheese.
A delightful blend of seafood served over a bed of fresh lettuce, decorated with generous amounts of tomatoes, mild Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese and black olives.
Two seafood enchiladas stuffed with flavorful seafood filling and covered with our special seafood sauce and creamy mozzarella cheese. Served with Spanish rice.

v_products_name_1: Wild caught fish or cod tacos
v_products_description_1: A savory duo of our grilled, wild-caught Alaskan salmon or lightly breaded cod served with mango pico de gallo and freshly chopped cilantro. Served with baja sauce, sour cream topping, lime wedge and a side of Spanish rice and fresh, seasoned and grilled vegetable mix.

We don't skimp on this enchilada! Our chef's special seafood filling, covered in a creamy seafood sauce and sprinkled with mozzarella cheese, stuffed in a large flour tortilla. Served with Spanish rice and your choice of beans.
Try our new wild-Alaskan salmon glazed with our house-made jalapeno jelly sauce. Served with grilled tomatoes, fresh mango pico de gallo and our seasoned and grilled vegetable mix.
A soft fresh tortilla and stuffed with our flavorful seafood filling, covered with our special seafood sauce, creamy Mozzarella cheese, fresh lettuce and diced tomatoes.

Your choice of four enchiladas: two hand-rolled enchiladas with your choice of meat paired with two of Paradiso’s famous Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese enchiladas and topped with our homemade sauce.
Bring your appetite! Choose from any three of our savory favorites, beef, chicken, pork carnitas or cheese enchiladas.  Add Spanish rice and your choice of beans for 1.49.
For the smaller appetite, enjoy a savory pair of beef, chicken, pork carnitas or cheese enchiladas.  Add Spanish rice and refried beans or fresh, seasoned and grilled vegetable mix for 1.49.
Your choice of beef, chicken, pork carnitas or cheese. Served with Spanish rice and your choice of beans. Substitute Spanish rice and beans with our fresh, seasoned and grilled vegetable mix for .99.

Morsels of seasoned lean pork marinated with savory herbs, spices and onions. Braised until tender and stuffed into a flour tortilla and covered with chile verde and melted cheese. Served with sour cream topping.
Muy Grande! It’s fully stuffed with your choice of meat, finished with our savory red sauce and melted Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese. It's the best!

There's only one way to make our burritos better - smother them in our incredible zesty cheese sauce and serve them with Spanish rice and your choice of beans. Choose beef or chicken. Substitute Spanish rice and beans with our fresh, seasoned and grilled vegetable mix for .99.

Sizzling tender steak or chicken strips with grilled onions and fresh poblano peppers, stuffed into a large flour tortilla and lavished with red sauce and melted Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese. Served with Spanish rice and sour cream topping.

Try this excellent combination of flavors! Mildly seasoned shredded chicken, broccoli and mozzarella cheese rolled into a warm tortilla and topped with our red sauce and melted Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese. Served with Spanish rice and a colorful blend of our fresh, seasoned and grilled vegetable mix.
A large flour tortilla wrapped around seasoned ground beef and refried beans, smothered with our homemade red sauce and melted Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese.

We're famous for this grande burrito stuffed with your choice of meat, refried beans and Spanish rice. Topped with red sauce, melted Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese and served with diced tomatoes, shredded lettuce and sour cream topping.

For the smaller appetite. A mini burrito filled with your choice of meat and covered with savory red sauce, topped with Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese. Served with a colorful blend of our fresh, seasoned and grilled vegetable mix, Spanish rice and your choice of beans.

Try a lighter version of our classic burrito!  This made to order burrito offers the flavors and ingredients you love: shredded lettuce, black beans, pico de gallo, Spanish rice and you choice of meat, all folded into a  warm flour tortilla then grilled.  Served with a side of creamy chipolte ranch dressing.

v_products_name_1: Jalapeno or Bean and Cheese Burrito
v_products_description_1: Your choice of a bean and cheese burrito or a bean and cheese burrito fired up with jalapeño peppers. Topped with mild Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese and our homemade red sauce.
Golden chicken breast tenderloins served with honey-mustard dipping sauce. Served with your choice of french fries or a chilled garden salad.
A piping hot bowl of our chicken tortilla soup served with a chilled side salad and breadstick.

Our juicy burger char-broiled the way you like it, topped with Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese. Garnished with Bermuda onion slices and pico de gallo. Served with your choice of french fries or a chilled garden salad.

One of lifes simple pleasures. A pair of crispy six inch corn tortillas, seasoned ground beef and savory shredded chicken with mild Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese and lettuce. Served with Spanish rice and beans.

A large flour tortilla stuffed with your choice of seasoned ground beef, shredded chicken or slow roasted carnitas.  Topped with Monterey Jack cheese, lettuce and sour cream topping. Served with a side of Spanish rice and your choice of beans.

Triple the taste with two large crunchy tacos and one soft taco filled with delicately seasoned ground beef, topped with mild Cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese. Served with Spanish rice and your choice of beans. Substitute Spanish rice and beans with our fresh, seasoned and grilled vegetable mix for .99.
